obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (29793)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes `1. 1st July, 1994, vide notification No. S.O. 491(E), dated1st July, 1994, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526&sectionId=29793&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Central Laws (Extension to`
  line `Arunachal Pradesh) Act, 1993.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on such date^1`
  line `as the Central Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, appoint.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (29794)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Extension of certain laws.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526&sectionId=29794&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `The Acts mentioned in the Schedule and all rules, orders, regulations`
  line `and schemes made thereunder are hereby extended to, and shall be in force in, the State of Arunachal`
  line Pradesh.
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (29795)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Construction of references to laws not in force in Arunachal Pradesh.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526&sectionId=29795&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `Any reference in any`
  line `Act, mentioned in the Schedule, to a law which is not in force in the State of Arunachal Pradesh shall, in`
  line `relation to that State, be construed as a reference to the corresponding law, if any, in force in that state.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (29796)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Construction of references to authorities where new authorities have been constituted.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526&sectionId=29796&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line Any
  line `reference by whatever form of words in any law for the time being in force in the State of Arunachal`
  line `Pradesh to any authority competent at the date of the passing of that law to exercise any powers or`
  line `discharge any functions in that State shall, where a corresponding new authority has been constituted by`
  line `or under any law now extended to that State, have effect as if it were a reference to the new authority.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (29797)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Power to remove difficulties.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526&sectionId=29797&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00016_199344_1517807323526
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `(1) If any difficulty arises in giving effect to the provisions of any`
  line `Act now extended to the State of Arunachal Pradesh, the Central Government may, by order notified in`
  line `the Official Gazette, make such provisions or give such directions as appear to it necessary for the`
  line `removal of the difficulty.`
  line
  line `(2) In particular, and without prejudice to the generality of the foregoing power, any such notified`
  line `order may,--`
  line
  line `(a) specify the corresponding authorities within the meaning of section 4;`
  line
  line `(b) provide for the transfer of any matter pending immediately before the commencement of`
  line `this Act before any court, tribunal or other authority, to any corresponding court, tribunal or other`
  line `authority for disposal:`
  line
  line `Provided that no such order shall be made after the expiry of two years from the date of`
  line `commencement of this Act.`
  line
  line `(3) Every order made under this section shall be laid before each House of Parliament.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
